race.description: Gordon Refrigeration Open Stake Pr1 Division1
race.comment: MISTER CADILLAC (1) can keep up the top recent form following a sharp 23.20 win two back with a OPEN victory at this track over 400m in 22.87. Flying lately and looks hard to top. JUST ALFIE (8) ran a lightning 22.78 winning a Grade 5 at this track over 400m last start. Expected to feature again. COMPTON COPY (7) was never in contention last time at Murray Bridge, but prior to that won by one length at this track (17.64) beating Typhoon Thomas in a Other on October 16. Great chance to atone. CADILLAC RAGTOP (5) racing over this distance brings the best out in her.
